habermas-mirror is a clean-room, prompted-only re-implementation of the
deliberation facilitator described in:

    Tessler, M. H., Bakker, M., Jarrett, D., et al.
    "AI can help humans find common ground in democratic deliberation."
    Science, 2024. doi:10.1126/science.adq2852

DeepMind's prompted reference implementation is published at
    https://github.com/google-deepmind/habermas_machine
and that repository is its own work under its own license.

habermas-mirror is NOT affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by
Google DeepMind, Alphabet, or the authors of the Science paper. The
fine-tuned reward model from the Science paper is not redistributed
here and is not derivable from this project.
